description: You've never seen this guy before, but we're pleased to show him off. He calls himself Rick Ravishing, and he's a 20 year old pizza delivery guy...so you might just see him in your neighborhood!For his debut scene, Rick will be getting down out in the jacuzzi, and then will be finishing himself off in front of the TV.Now remember, this is his first scene ever, but we were lucky enough to convince this guy to experiment with his sexuality, so stay tuned!Enjoy!
title: Rick Ravishing
